      <h3 style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text-bright,#fff);margin-bottom:12px">Data Sources & Methodology</h3>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-dim,#94a3b8);line-height:1.7;margin:0">ETF data sourced from fund prospectuses, SEC filings, and financial data aggregators. Expense ratios, holdings, and performance figures are updated periodically and may reflect slight delays from official filings.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="max-width:800px;margin:40px auto;padding:0 24px">
    <div style="background:var(--card-bg,#0a1020);border:1px solid var(--border-color,#152040);border-radius:12px;padding:24px">
      <h3 style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text-dim,#94a3b8);margin-bottom:8px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.5px">Cite This Page</h3>
      <code style="display:block;background:var(--bg-color,#060a12);padding:16px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-primary,#c8d0de);font-family:monospace;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">Westmount Fundamentals. "QQQ vs QQQM: Expense Ratio & Comparison Tool." westmountfundamentals.com/qqq-vs-qqqm, 2026.</code>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="max-width:800px;margin:40px auto;padding:0 24px">
    <h2 style="font-size:20px;color:var(--text-bright,#fff);margin-bottom:16px">Related Pages</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:12px">
      <a href="/qqq-vs-sp500/" style="display:block;padding:16px;background:var(--card-bg,#0a1020);border:1px solid var(--border-color,#152040);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text-primary,#c8d0de);transition:transform 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='none'">QQQ vs S&P 500: Compare Index Funds & Performance</a>
      <a href="/qqq-etf-review-2026/" style="display:block;padding:16px;background:var(--card-bg,#0a1020);border:1px solid var(--border-color,#152040);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text-primary,#c8d0de);transition:transform 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='none'">QQQ ETF Review (2026): Invesco Nasdaq 100 Holdings</a>
      <a href="/stock-split-calculator/" style="display:block;padding:16px;background:var(--card-bg,#0a1020);border:1px solid var(--border-color,#152040);border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--text-primary,#c8d0de);transition:transform 0.2s" onmouseover="this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'" onmouseout="this.style.transform='none'">Stock Split Calculator & Guide: How Forward and Reverse Spli</a>
